      "content": "It's a heavy and exhausting feeling to keep trying when you're already so worn down. That feeling of being fundamentally broken is a very real and understandable place to be. If you're feeling this empty, perhaps it's time to stop trying to fix things and just let yourself be still. Reaching out to a therapist or counselor can provide a safe space to explore these feelings without judgment.",
